title: I got a S- but no chest

embed.description: Snaggy is an image hosting service that lets you paste images from your clipboard directly online.

replies.body:
Hey Alexcious,

Just a head's up, only you can see your letter grade for a match, even if you link the match details to someone else!

Please check your **Collection** tab to verify that you haven't already received a box for Fiora this season. The box-eligibility per-champion will not reset until the beginning of the 2018 season in January. (Source: Red Poster "Broporo" in another thread)

You can tell if a champion has already received an S-chest by rather or not they have a border around their portrait.

Ex: https://i.imgur.com/iq9VYsv.png
In this image, an S-Chest has already been claimed for Janna in the 2017 season, but Lux is still elgible.

Hope that helps :)
